SIMPLE: brightly
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Brightly
<hw>Bright"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Brilliantly;
splendidly; with luster; <as>as, <ex>brightly</ex> shining
armor</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>With lively intelligence; intelligently.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Looking <qex>brightly</qex> into the mother's face.</q>
<rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brightness</ent>⟦br⟧
